content: I haven't found a better retirement calculator. This one hits the mark!!!

This app is good for someone who has a very traditional situation and is completely unfamiliar with the benefits and costs of retirement, and how to look them up. The only part that I found beneficial was the disability rating options. It didn't help with calculatuons for former spouse receiving a portion of retirement or SBP in a more custom amount. I'm glad it didn't cost more, and definitely feel like it wasn't worth the price for my situation.
Perfect
Always informative
Great application
Excellent app. Would give 5 stars if it included less than 20 years of service for those facing forced early retirement.
Great app, easy to use. I would put Six stars if you guys go a step beyond and add in states.
Wow - impressive and easy to use. Instead of your buddy's handmade spreadsheet, this has all the up to date premiums and insurance costs and taxes. I recommend it
This is a great app and I highly recommend it to anyone that is trying to figure out what they could or will make when they retire. Well worth the little amount of money this app costs!
Great app
Algorithms need to be updated for pay
very useful

Works great. East to set up, view, compare, and edit multiple profiles. I set it up to show what I should expect to receive if I retire at 20 years at my current rank, 23 years (high three) at the rank I'll likely be promoted to a couple months before the 20 year mark, and the next rank with both 26 and 30 years to compare. Never had any issues. I'd rather PAY for an app without adds and potetial privacy compromising permission any day! Thanks, and keep up the great work!
Retired 1 Sept 2019. The amounts for payment were within 2% range of what I actually received.
(Update) thanks for creating the tool! //// Needs a tool to calculate pay based on 2 different grades during final 3 yrs of service.
Very buggy. Unable to switch between saved configurations... unable to open certain windows to affect changes. For a $6 app you would expect it to work.
Great info pulled from a few different areas relevant to eventual retirement income. Nicely presented and easy to use.
love the app, except, it doesn't calculate years of service/years of pay. Thanks, Mr. Alger.
tera can start at 15 yrs and it wont allow you to choose 15 to 20 yrs in order to see the money you will get if you were to fall into any of the months berween the 15 and 20
Straight forward layout makes ease of use. At the time I downloaded the app, I noticed some spelling errors, which will probably be fixed as soon as the developer reads this review.
I love the app! If it's accurate I will encourage all of my friends to get it.
love it!

Concise and to the point. Most accurate app of its type and definitely 
worth the price of a beer. Gives nearly exact dollar amounts for everything 
that influences my pay in retirement and is indispensable for financial 
planning. Fantastic job!
Great App. Very accurate!
